*odbc_field_len*

(PHP 4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)

odbc_field_len â€” Get the length (precision) of a field

===============================================================================
[ Description ]

  odbc_field_len(Odbc\Result $statement, int $field): int|false~

Gets the length of the field referenced by number in the given result
identifier.

===============================================================================
[ Parameters ]

{statement}

  The ODBC result object.

{field}

  The field number. Field numbering starts at 1.

===============================================================================
[ Return Values ]

Returns the field length, or false on error.

===============================================================================
